{"tid":317333,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日公司嚟咗個新同事 我即刻畀個下馬威佢","createTime":"2017-07-11T11:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T23:51:58.000Z","uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"159b6bff339adb2ab3a47780bdb946a3a85b1d1b","tid":317333,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n公司空降咗個分店副經理<br />\n無啦啦有個新仔騎住你就梗係唔gur啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我地就一齊出去食lunch歡迎下佢咁啦<br />\n我就順手幫佢斟茶<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢個時候佢竟然講唔該!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我心諗 而家啲後生係咪咁廢呀 <br />\n敲檯呢啲基本禮儀都唔識<br />\n<br />\n所謂新官上任三把火 我梗係畀個下馬威佢啦<br />\n即刻鬧到佢面懵懵<br />\n<br />\n睇怕佢以後都唔咁郁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00de1e53d94fe167658a551215e3fb70d07517a","tid":317333,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7943f0896a308ebcf6463bedca972b1899dc554","tid":317333,"uid":110298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://y2.pichunter.com/3441993_6_o.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fy2.pichunter.com%2F3441993_6_o.jpg&d=%2BorDB%2BNLk3YiV8Fdp8gYIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e5debfaa\" target=\"_blank\">http://y2.pichunter.com/3441993_6_o.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a9b05e2f96726be412ce7b73f96959a834c017","tid":317333,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://y2.pichunter.com/3441993_6_o.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fy2.pichunter.com%2F3441993_6_o.jpg&d=%2BorDB%2BNLk3YiV8Fdp8gYIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e5debfaa\" targe